-- U.K. Stocks Erase Losses; Mining Companies Antofagasta, Xstrata Advance
-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 2010-09-22T13:38:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/u-k-stocks-erase-losses-mining-companies-antofagasta-xstrata-advance.html
U.K. stocks erased losses, led by a
rally in mining companies.  The FTSE 100 Index rose 0.1 percent to 5,583.58 at 2:35
p.m. in London after earlier falling as much as 1.1 percent.  Antofagasta Plc, Xstrata Plc and Kazakhmys Plc all climbed
more than 3 percent in London trading.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sarah Jones at 
 sjones35@bloomberg.net  